@startuml
start

:Input & Configuration;
:Load existing KB (optional);

:Source Discovery & Filtering;
:Traverse directory, infer language, exclude irrelevant files;

:KPI Candidate Extraction;
:Scan files for signal-driven and structure-based KPI patterns;
:Collect KPI name, file, line, context, formula;

:Ranking & Selection;
:Rank candidates by signal strength;

:KB Enrichment & Conflict Resolution;
:Merge with KB, resolve conflicts, create stubs for new KPIs;

:AI-Assisted Narrative Creation;
:Generate description, explain formula, infer units, categorize, score;

:Interactive Bluebook Rendering;
:Render KPI data, code snippet, deep link, edit option;

:Review, Edit, & Maintain;
:Stakeholders review, edit, comment, persist to KB;

:Regeneration with Continuity;
:On code changes, repeat process, merge new/modified KPIs;

stop
@enduml
